THE LEGENDARY RIDER'S JOURNEY

Born in a small mountain village, our hero grew up with a single dream: to conquer the world's most challenging hills and earn the legendary XRider title.

Starting with an old motorcycle, this brave rider uses gold earned from each race to buy new vehicles and challenge increasingly dangerous tracks.

"Every hill is a challenge, every descent is a victory! Become part of this legend!"
